                  </hi>. I am shopman to Mr. Kennedy, of high-street, shad well, a pawnbroker. This watch was pawned by the prisoner on the 15th of December.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370102-name-622" type="witnessName">
